snippet.title: Allison's Diary: Rebirth - Xbox Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Allison's Diary: Rebirth is a first person survival horror, where you will have to search for the truth while exploring realistic and graphically stunning environments, facing terrible enemies and scary jump scares.


Web site:
http://www.krgames.it

Microsoft store (Windows and Xbox):
https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/p/allisons-diary-rebirth/9MWPD4G2CM56?activetab=pivot:overviewtab
